'''DetonatioN Rising''' was the academy team of [[DetonatioN FocusMe]].

== History ==
[[DetonatioN Gaming]] acquired a challenger team on May 12 2016 to compete in the [[LJL_Challenger_Series/2016_Season/Summer_Season|LJL Challenger Series]]. The team was formed with [[strider (Haruki Yamaguchi)|strider]] and [[Gariaru]] from [[Saikyo Makinyan]], [[Astarore]] from [[DetonatioN FocusMe]], [[Muzyura]], and [[R C]].

